nary observer's frame it is found that the radiation becomes oblique\nagainst the magnetic field. For approaching holes the radiated frequencies may\neven exceed the local electron cyclotron frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2011 18:15:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2011 11:44:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-17"}
