ergies > 4 Ry to generate the observed amount of\nmid-infrared emission in our sample of BAT AGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2011 20:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
